    • Constructor Detail

      • CTSWorkerTask

        public CTSWorkerTask​(CTSWorkerQuery query,
                     CTSWorkerProcess process,
                     CTSWorkerFilter filter,
                     String name)
        Worker task constructor, requiring a query which selects elements to be processed, a process defining the strategy for those elements, and a filter to remove elements to which the strategy should not be applied.
        Parameters:
        query - The query to be performed against the data layer.
        process - The process to apply to filtered results from the executed query.
        filter - The filter to use to reduce the set returned from the executed query.
        name - The name by which this task can be identified. This is currently used to name the thread on which this task is run.
